			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The real &quot;low-down&quot; on the Scimitar:<BR>
<BR>
1)  Its hard to get to, the foreman room is deep in Sol A, and my party (4 lvl 20-25s) couldn't do it without some help.<BR>
<BR>
2)  The foreman was yellow/red to me at lvl 21.<BR>
<BR>
3)  The worst part about being down there are the wizards, saw two take out our lvl20 monk in no time flat.  &quot;I've never seen someone's hitpoints disappear so fast!&quot;  - Duncaan<BR>
<BR>
4)  One runs and your party should vacate immediately.<BR>
<BR>
5)  The scimitar is nice, the stats are correct and it dropped the 3rd time we slaughtered the foreman.<BR>
<BR>
6)  Our party - 20 Monk, 21 War, 25 War, 22 Druid<BR>
<BR>
7)  Secondary loot off Foreman is the Foreman's Tunic, nice item worth something like 300pp or so.  Not too shabby secondary loot.  AC10 +3 STR +3 WIS.<BR>
<BR>
Baynesong<BR>
22 Circle Warrior, MM
